<p>The University has perfected this distinction. Thanks to our advancements in natural philosophy, no one need ever fear a slave or wife who has transgressed the bounds of orthoskepsi.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>- <a href="/address-to-the-students-and-faculty">Address to the Students and Faculty</a></p>
<blockquote>
<p>Murdering your peers beforehand, while not technically against any rules, goes against the spirit of the election.<br />
Similarly, negating the event of their birth should be looked down upon, though substantially less so.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>- <a href="/empty-unmarked-grave">Empty Unmarked Grave</a></p>
