<p>- <a href="/scp-3108">SCP-3108</a></p>
<blockquote>
<p>The sculptor sculpted, and I burnt. People like me, I see why you wanna lock us up sometimes. I really fucking do, buddy.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>- <a href="/scp-3420">SCP-3420</a></p>
<blockquote>
<p>I feel so old now. The young have a fire inside of them that I used to have. But I used to be fire, too. I remember the flame that bloomed inside of me. When you tap into that, you start to see that moral codes are kind of bullshit.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>- <a href="/scp-4669">SCP-4669</a></p>
