<h1 id="toc22"><span>Office For The Reclamation of Islamic Artifacts (ORIA)</span></h1>
<div style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://imgur.com/2tawPGT.png" style="width:25%;" alt="2tawPGT.png" class="image" /></div>
